metadata.name: bustling street in the rain
metadata.description: Created with the help of artificial intelligence, this NFT captures the energy of a busy city street on a rainy day, with crowds of people rushing by and colorful umbrellas creating a vibrant sea of movement. The headlights and taillights of passing cars leave glowing trails in the rain, adding to the sense of hustle and bustle. The mood is dim, moody and atmospheric, with intricate details that give the scene a stylized, posed and dark look. The artwork evokes a sense of the vibrancy and excitement of urban life, even in the midst of a downpour, and showcases the creative collaboration between the artist and AI technology.
